**Body:**
    
    
    {
        "labels": [
            { "classId": 0, "bbox": [0.5, 0.5, 0.2, 0.3] },
            { "classId": 1, "segments": [0.1, 0.2, 0.3, 0.2, 0.2, 0.4] }
